zon.com%2FASTRO-Gaming-Wired-Headset-Audio-Xbox%2Fdp%2FB07NSRYDH9" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/ASTRO-Gaming-Wired-Headset-Audio-Xbox/dp/B07NSRYDH9?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">Astro A40 TR</a>的售价为 100 美元，比平时的市场价格低 30 美元，是我们见过的最低价格。 A40 TR 是我们<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-gaming-headset-130006477.html">最佳游戏耳机</a>指南中的首选，因为其开放式设计赋予其比大多数竞争对手更宽敞、更具包围感的声音。它强调低音，但不会达到压倒性的程度，而且长时间佩戴也很舒适。也就是说，内置麦克风还不错，就像任何开放式耳机一样，整个耳机都会泄漏并让大量外部噪音进入，所以如果你通常在吵闹的房间里玩，它并不理想。一般来说，除非您需要麦克风，否则您可以从一副“普通”有线耳机获得比专用游戏耳机更好的价值。不过，如果您确实想要一款一体化解决方案，A40 TR 是一个值得妥协的选择。</p><h2>三星 Pro Plus </h2><p><core-commerce id="c1bad010cff64680ab71fb725c669787" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEMxUFQ5WFhTP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTF1My0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiYzk2MmY4M2YtYWVhMS00NjRlLTkwYmMtOWM4YzczY2MyZDU5In0&amp;signature=AQAAAVebJ72EN7VieRArOXmqgUaU6MimJJo6mK6EPlgR-52J&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0C1PT9XXS" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0C1PT9XXS?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">三星 Pro Plus</a>是我们<a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-microsd-card-130038282.html">microSD 卡购买指南</a>中的首选，目前其 128GB、256GB 和 512GB 型号分别降至<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRj